<header class="masthead bg-primary text-white text-center">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="shop">
    <img class="img-fluid mb-5 d-block mx-auto" src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2018/04/24/Cl8ivt.png" alt="">
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-uppercase mb-0">人航财务支付辅助系统</h1>
    <h2 class="font-weight-light mb-0">对外汇款请先注册登陆后填写相关付款信息</h2>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- Services -->
    <section id="services">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
            <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase">系统功能介绍</h2>
            <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">关于人航财务付款报销的相关事宜</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row text-center">
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
              <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
              <i class="fa fa-shopping-cart fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>

            </span>
            <h4 class="service-heading"><li><%= link_to("对外付款", groups_path) %></li></h4>
            <p class="text-muted">点击进入支付系统，点击右上角的我要付款，按照顺序填写收款人、账号、汇入地省份、汇入行名称、金额、用途、经办人，所有项目都需要填写，不能为空</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
              <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
              <i class="fa fa-laptop fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
            </span>
            <h4 class="service-heading"><li><%= link_to("常用下载", resumes_path) %></li></h4>
            <p class="text-muted">可下载常用的支出凭单、支票领用单、打车票据报销单等</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4">
            <span class="fa-stack fa-4x">
              <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i>
              <i class="fa fa-lock fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>
            </span>
            <h4 class="service-heading"><li><%= link_to("付款步骤图", about_index_path) %></li></h4>
            <p class="text-muted">点击查看快速了解付款步骤，了解付款中需提供相关的发票及报销单。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
